data.description: LIKE NEW. BETTER THAN NEW. CLEAN AS A WHISTLE. VERY WELL TAKEN CARE OF! BUILT IN 2020, THIS TRI-LEVEL HOME OFFERS A DESIGNER BEAUTIFUL KITCHEN, 4 BEDROOMS WITH SPACE FOR A 5TH BEDROOM, 3 Full BATHROOMS PLUS A 1/2 BATHROOM (TOTAL OF 4 BATHROOMS), A LARGE FULLY FENCED BACK YARD, AND A 2-CAR GARAGE. VERY FAMILY FRIENDLY HOME. TWO BEDROOMS UP AND TWO BEDROOMS DOWN. THE HOUSE COULD VERY EASILY ACCOMODATE A 5TH BEDROOMS AS IT HAS THE SPACE AND LAYOUT. ONE OF THE LOWER BEDROOMS HAS 220 VOLT AND COULD EVEN BE A SECOND FAMILY OR GAME ROOM. THE STAINLESS-STEEL KITCHEN HAS A HIGHY UPGARDED COUNTER DEPTH REFRIGERATOR, LARGE PANTRY, AND LVP FLOORING WITH SEPARATE DINING AREA. THE LARGE LAUNDRY ROOM IS CONVENIENTLY LOCATED ON THE UPPER FLOOR WITH THE MASTER BEDROOM. THE HIGH CEILINGS AND THE CHOICE OF COLORS MAKE FOR A MODERN BEAUTIFUL FLOW. CENTRAL A/C AND AUTOMATIC SPRINKLER SYSTEM INCLUDED. COVERED COMPOSITE DECKING ENTRY, PATIO IN REAR, CLOSE TO PARK, SHOPS, RESTAURANTS, AND SCHOOL, AND A DIRECT SHOT UP MARKSHEFFEL TO PETERSON AIRFORCE BASE AND VERY NEAR FORT CARSON.
